---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Pricing — In Parallel" description="Start free with the AI note-taker. Add a Living Plan when you're ready. Simple, transparent pricing." navTheme="light">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-44 md:pb-32 bg-white text-ip-navy">
    <div class="container-ip max-w-5xl">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight mb-4 text-ip-navy">Pricing</h1>
        <p class="text-ip-navy/60 text-lg max-w-[52ch] mx-auto">Start free with the AI note-taker. Add the Living Plan when you're ready to turn meeting signals into execution.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing Cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <!-- Free — AI Note-Taker -->
        <div class="border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm flex flex-col">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-2 text-ip-navy">AI Note-Taker</h2>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm mb-6">Per user, monthly</p>
          <div class="mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy/30 line-through decoration-ip-navy/20">&euro;9</span>
            <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-ip-navy">&euro;0</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-8">free forever for qualified customers &mdash; no credit card required</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-ip-navy/70 text-sm mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Joins meetings silently (Zoom, Teams, Meet)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Transcribes with speaker attribution
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Instant, structured summaries
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Extracts decisions, risks, commitments
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Zero friction — no behavior change
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/waitlist" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">
            Start for free
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Living Plan (highlighted) -->
        <div class="border-2 border-ip-blue rounded-xl p-8 bg-white shadow-md relative flex flex-col">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-ip-blue text-white text-xs font-display px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Recommended</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-2 text-ip-navy">Living Plan</h2>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm mb-6">Per scope, monthly</p>
          <div class="mb-1">
            <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-ip-navy">&euro;39–69</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-8">per scope / month · commitment tiers below</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-ip-navy/70 text-sm mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Everything in Free, plus:
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Auto-updates plan from meeting signals
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Priority recalculation in real-time
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Drift detection — divergence from plan
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Integrations with PM, CRM, OKR tools
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-ip-navy/8">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              DPA included &mdash; GDPR-ready out of the box
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              EU data residency &mdash; nothing leaves Europe
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              Configurable data retention policies
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-blue mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              No model training on your data &mdash; ever
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/demo" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">
            Book a demo
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Enterprise / Custom -->
        <div class="border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm relative flex flex-col">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-ip-navy/8 text-ip-navy/50 text-xs font-display px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Coming soon</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-2 text-ip-navy">Enterprise</h2>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm mb-6">Custom pricing</p>
          <div class="mb-1">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy/40">Custom</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-8">tailored to your organization</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-ip-navy/40 text-sm mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Everything in Living Plan, plus:
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              MCP Context Platform — APIs for AI agents
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Leadership &amp; coaching skills
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Decision velocity & follow-through metrics
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              Risk & compliance intelligence
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-ip-navy/8">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              SSO &amp; SCIM provisioning
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              Full audit logs &amp; access controls
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              Custom data retention &amp; deletion policies
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ip-navy/20 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              DPIA documentation &amp; dedicated security review
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/demo" class="text-ip-navy/40 border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-display inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full hover:border-ip-navy/30 transition-colors">
            Talk to us
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Living Plan Commitment Tiers -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ip-navy mb-2 text-center">Living Plan tiers</h2>
        <p class="text-ip-navy/50 text-sm text-center mb-8">Longer commitment, lower price. All tiers include the same features.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <!-- Flexible -->
          <div class="border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-6 bg-white">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-1">Flexible</h3>
            <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-4">Month-to-month</p>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy">&euro;69</span>
              <span class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm"> / scope / mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ip-navy/60 text-xs">
              <li>No minimum commitment</li>
              <li>No minimum volume</li>
              <li>Pilots &amp; small teams</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <!-- Annual (recommended) -->
          <div class="border-2 border-ip-blue rounded-xl p-6 bg-white relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-2.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
              <span class="bg-ip-blue text-white text-[10px] font-display px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Best value</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-1">Annual</h3>
            <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-4">12-month commitment</p>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy">&euro;59</span>
              <span class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm"> / scope / mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ip-navy/60 text-xs">
              <li>No minimum scope requirement</li>
              <li>Primary commercial tier</li>
              <li>Most popular choice</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <!-- Multi-Year -->
          <div class="border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-6 bg-white">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-1">Multi-Year</h3>
            <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-4">24-month commitment</p>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy">&euro;49</span>
              <span class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm"> / scope / mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ip-navy/60 text-xs">
              <li>Minimum 10 scopes</li>
              <li>Multi-team rollouts</li>
              <li>PMO-driven deployments</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <!-- Strategic Enterprise -->
          <div class="border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-6 bg-white">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-1">Strategic Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-ip-navy/40 text-xs mb-4">36-month commitment</p>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-ip-navy">&euro;39</span>
              <span class="text-ip-navy/40 text-sm"> / scope / mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-ip-navy/60 text-xs">
              <li>Minimum 25 scopes</li>
              <li>Portfolio-wide adoption</li>
              <li>Optional onboarding support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Volume + ROI callout -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-ip-navy/[0.03] border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-8 text-center flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-2">500+ scopes? Volume discounts.</p>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/50 text-sm">Large-scale deployments get custom pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-ip-navy/[0.03] border border-ip-navy/10 rounded-xl p-8 text-center flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="font-display text-lg text-ip-navy mb-2">Typical payback: under 1 week</p>
          <p class="text-ip-navy/50 text-sm">~10&times; ROI vs monthly scope cost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Small Print -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-6 text-ip-navy">The small print</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-ip-navy/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>The AI Note-Taker is free for qualified customers with no credit card required. Living Plan pricing is per execution scope per month.</p>
          <p>All prices provided herewith are strictly bound to the In Parallel <a href="/general-terms-of-service" class="text-ip-blue underline decoration-ip-blue/30 hover:decoration-ip-blue">General Terms and Conditions</a>.</p>
          <p>Prices exclude any possible value-added taxes, local taxes, or duties.</p>
          <p>The payment term is 30 days from the invoice date. Late payment charges are defined in the service <a href="/general-terms-of-service" class="text-ip-blue underline decoration-ip-blue/30 hover:decoration-ip-blue">Terms and Conditions</a>.</p>
          <p>The currency used is EUR. In Parallel reserves the right to modify pricing from time to time and it will reflect all agreements (after commitment term) and offers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-ip-navy text-white">
    <div class="container-ip text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight mb-4">Not sure which plan fits?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-8 max-w-[52ch] mx-auto">Start free with the AI note-taker. When you're ready for the Living Plan, we'll help you find the right setup.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/waitlist" class="btn-primary">
          Start for free
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/demo" class="btn-secondary">
          Book a demo
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
